page.title: 05RECTOR'S WIFE 1985
page.content:
RELIGON Mrs Robinson has been a Rector's wife for 7 years.She runs Sunday school,she does the flowers in the church,she runs the over sixties group.She also does cleaning and visits people.She doesn't enjoy any of these things.Its very hard work. She doesn't go to all the church services.Her house is 25 years old. Its called the Rectory.There are no other vicars in her family.She has 2 boy's.She has a dog,a cat,2 sheep, 2 lambs and 2 fish.She has been living in Bentworth for 3 years. She likes the people very much.
by Lizze & Karen.
